title: THE DIRECTION SERIES. No.1.  COURTESY  AND RUDENESS  01-12-15
description:
"The twenty first century, despite its bewilderment, still allows permission to those 
few who will pay the price of not lessening human life. This possibility the 
Eminent Way has not failed and out of respect for itself declares it's criteria and 
the freedom of its particular path. By this can others freely include or freely 
exclude themselves as is always the case."

Leo
